ns and queries. Thank You.\n\nDate: Today (January 21, 2023), Saturday\nTime: 4-6 PM.\nTopic: SIU BSA Career Counseling\nTime: Jan 21, 2023 04:00 PM Central Time (US and Canada)\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting\nhttps://zoom.us/j/95350551523\n\nMeeting ID: 953 5055 1523\nOne tap mobile\n+13126266799,,95350551523# US (Chicago)\n+13092053325,,95350551523# US\n\nSumaiya Binta Islam\nPresident', 'Greetings Everyone,\n\nGood afternoon. BSA is planning to organize a career development seminar where we, as international students will be able to know the procedure and steps to get into the job field after finishing Masters/PhD. There will be three speakers, Riaheen Farzana, Assistant Professor of Business Administration; Kuntal Ghosh, Senior Consultant, Supply Chain, EVista and Mostak Ahmed Shumon, PhD Candidate, Department of Mathematics, SIUC to cover both Academia and industry sectors. It will be conducted over zoom (online) so that everyone can join. Zoom link has been attached to this email. Hoping this session will meet your expectations and queries. Thank You.\n\nDate: Today (January 21, 2023), Saturday\nTime: 4-6 PM.\nTopic: SIU BSA Career Counseling\nTime: Jan 21, 2023 04:00 PM Central Time (US and Canada)\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting\nhttps://zoom.us/j/95350551523\n\nMeeting ID: 953 5055 1523\nOne tap mobile\n+13126266799,,95350551523# US (Chicago)\n+13092053325,,95350551523# US\n\nSumaiya Binta Islam\nPresident', '', None, datetime.datetime(2023, 1, 21, 12, 35, 8), 1674326108, None, 'https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An_UvxJXg9tdnLU3Y5qjPi0200MLilhzPXUgxzGjQzUMaNcmjdZA6anyrngvkdub33NZzZhd51fpCAEzNHFhko5aKRFP5fS1w_lKwYrzcNLupv27.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBaIyI1GghPTHlZudMsYtMW_pWuCi6_JPXo0hOvwZ0xIg&oe=65761BB9&_nc_sid=7da55a', [], [], ['https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An_UvxJXg9tdnLU3Y5qjPi0200MLilhzPXUgxzGjQzUMaNcmjdZA6anyrngvkdub33NZzZhd51fpCAEzNHFhko5aKRFP5fS1w_lKwYrzcNLupv27.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBaIyI1GghPTHlZudMsYtMW_pWuCi6_JPXo0hOvwZ0xIg&oe=65761BB9&_nc_sid=7