great. I will be starting my PhD in CS program this Spring semester. I will be joining the lab directed by Professor Dr. Talukder Sajedul Karim.\n\nMy flight to Carbondale is on 20th January. My spouse and kid faced interview today and have been approved. They will be in Carbondale within next 2 months if everything goes well. Now I am seeking suggestion regarding housing in Carbondale.\n\nWhat are the available housing options suitable for family of 3, like I heard little about Ambassador Hall, Bryan's house (if am not wrong), Evergreen Terrace etc.\n\nPlease suggest me which would be suitable for me. TIA", "Assalamualaikum everyone,\n\nI hope you all are doing great. I will be starting my PhD in CS program this Spring semester. I will be joining the lab directed by Professor Dr. Talukder Sajedul Karim.\n\nMy flight to Carbondale is on 20th January. My spouse and kid faced interview today and have been approved. They will be in Carbondale within next 2 months if everything goes well. Now I am seeking suggestion regarding housing in Carbondale.\n\nWhat are the available housing options suitable for family of 3, like I heard little about Ambassador Hall, Bryan's house (if am not wrong), Evergreen Terrace etc.\n\nPlease suggest me which would be suitable for me. TIA", '', None, datetime.datetime(2023, 1, 8, 12, 40, 10), 1673203210, None, 'https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An_UvxJXg9tdnLU3Y5qjPi0200MLilhzPXUgxzGjQzUMaNcmjdZA6anyrngvkdub33NZzZhd51fpCAEzNHFhko5aKRFP5fS1w_lKwYrzcNLupv27.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBaIyI1GghPTHlZudMsYtMW_pWuCi6_JPXo0hOvwZ0xIg&oe=65761BB9&_nc_sid=7da55a', [], [], ['https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An_UvxJXg9tdnLU3Y5qjPi0200MLilhzPXUgxzGjQzUMaNcmjdZA6anyrngvkdub33NZzZhd51fpCAEzNHFhko5aKRFP5fS1w_lKwYrzcNLupv27.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBaIyI1GghPTHlZudMsYtMW_pWuCi6_JPXo0hOvwZ0xIg&oe=65761BB9&_nc_sid=7da55a'], ['Like'], None, None, None, None, None, None, None, None, None, 1, 12, 0, 'https://m.facebook.com/groups/1590338747870221/pe