EHbATJysCzg&__tn__=C-R&paipv=0&eav=AfaNY3IEDq-BtbYTy93u8G_x1-0HHTfxBZmCRlgkm9V-IbCeLjoakizIQCYfqvtuwQE'}], '108975778686264', None, '491555839674054', ['491555839674054'], False, 'Ramesh Neupane\u200eBangladesh Student Association SIUC (BSA)'])dict_values(['3309291159308296', "Carbondale is where education, culture, and nature come together. We are located in one of the region's most picturesque areas on the edge of the 280,000- acre Shawnee National Forest, and minutes away from Crab Orchard National Wildlife Refuge, and many recreational lakes. With the Shawnee National Forest as its backdrop, our neck of the woods is unique in many ways. There are approximately 150 different species of native trees on the SIU campus in Carbondale. SIU has earned national recognition for its Tree Campus Higher Education program since 2015. Here is my attempt to capture some of the glimpses of our beautiful 1,133 acres campus posted on my youtube channel 🙂\n\nYOUTUBE.COM\nSouthern Illinois University Tour | SIU Carbondale Fall Foliage | 4K", "Carbondale is where education, culture, and nature come together. We are located in one of the region's most picturesque areas on the edge of the 280,000- acre Shawnee National Forest, and minutes away from Crab Orchard National Wildlife Refuge, and many recreational lakes. With the Shawnee National Forest as its backdrop, our neck of the woods is unique in many ways. There are approximately 150 different species of native trees on the SIU campus in Carbondale. SIU has earned national recognition for its Tree Campus Higher Education program since 2015. Here is my attempt to capture some of the glimpses of our beautiful 1,133 acres campus posted on my youtube channel 🙂", 'YOUTUBE.COM\nSouthern Illinois University Tour | SIU Carbondale Fall Foliage | 4K', None, datetime.datetime(2022, 10, 27, 9, 45, 17), 1666881917, None, 'https://external-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/emg1/v/t13/8212786232080722822?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F0hpKkdsP48I%2Fmaxre