J3FVWtIWDXlD1gk3EI3-WKzExFfhUf2sMlVfQv0zFANRUQZt3MjicZ7X-MpnMee3zLcoRwL7ppWI_x46txthzKhfXgGuxMJz_dc43jp3l9l3lcVnbVKwo9ivjBMim7YfKcSWGS48jEkyVsjiSEOrRuuSNiFqnQmVJdhdR52UcQmAp38cTf8PA9WoqVSptoiIIS9ztmSuXMU_ZPVYMFr2xxQXiwn7PNuJgPXhqWH5YA_oQm51l855g9sNgtmwDcp5wm6egASqccD6n0AHxcFAWTLsaU3GIBHybzTA5WqeU7kh6XGBbAkDrH7hg8YXQSXi9norDM7gN8eSs1aMKoYivIziFtu4jRZIsZAfGD4B-5o1ph0R3Az47FTADAh4WRApyxNq7XOuG2Q1ZG-vFqh2d2cNg&__tn__=C-R&paipv=0&eav=Afb4BuZyoqVLlmYleA-PBueWvNxqvOa0prhMiCUh31kPJk1Dp7DJPu5_lve_RmPlJzI'}], None, None, None, [], False, 'Jawad Siddique Efaz\u200eBangladesh Student Association SIUC (BSA)'])dict_values(['3303340829903329', "AN important email from University. Do not miss the last para. So please please register everyone:\n\nGood Morning Salukis!\n\nThis email serves as a final reminder to register and attend Saturday's Student Leadership Conference!\n\n8:00 a.m. - 8:40 am Check-In and continental breakfast\n8:45-3:00 pm Conference | Lunch and snacks will be provided.\nLocation: Student Center\n\nJoin us for a day of strengthening your leadership skills. Gain personal competencies in management, communication, teamwork, time management, strategic planning, proactive event planning, goal setting, and more! Better understand your ability to work with others and about one's own identity and engagement. Our keynote speakers will be Ana Larrea-Albert and Dr. Walter Kimbrough. Food will be provided. Registration closes today at 11:00 am; you can register at the following link: https://siu.presence.io/form/student-leadership-conference-registration. The conference is free for all registrants.\n\nBy courtesy of the Vice Chancellor for Student Affairs and Vice Chancellor for Antiracism, Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion, an $1,000 award will be given to the top RSO(s) (RSOs of 10 members or more) that have the highest percentage of membership in attendance to go toward leadership development programming. The top RSO(s) (less than 10 members) will receive $500 toward leadership development programming.\n\nSIU.PRESENCE.IO\nSouthern Illinois University", "AN important email from University. Do not miss the last para. So please please register everyone:\n\nGood Morning Salukis!\n\nThis email serves as a final reminder to register and attend Saturday's Student Leadership Conference!\n\n8:00 a.m. - 8:40 am Check-In and continental breakfast\n8:45-3:00 pm Conference | Lunch and snacks will be provided.\nLocation: Student Center\n\nJoin us for a day of strengthening your leadership skills. Gain personal competencies in management, communication, teamwork, time management, strategic planning, proactive event planning, goal setting, and more! Better understand your ability to work with others and about one's own identity and engagement. Our keynote speakers will be Ana Larrea-Albert and Dr. Walter Kimbrough. Food will be provided. Registration closes today at 11:00 am; you can register at the following link: https://siu.presence.io/form/student-leadership-conference-registration. The conference is free for all registrants.\n\nBy courtesy of the Vice Chancellor for Student Affairs and Vice Chancellor for Antiracism, Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion, an $1,000 award will be given to the top RSO(s) (RSOs of 10 members or more) that have the highest percentage of membership in attendance to go toward leadership development programming. The top RSO(s) (less than 10 members) will receive $500 toward leadership development programming.", 'SIU.PRESENCE.IO\nSouthern Illinois University', None, datetime.datetime(2022, 10, 20, 10, 48, 54), 1666280934, None, 'https://external-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/emg1/v/t13/11125400941212911005?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcheckimhere.blob.core.windows.net%2Fcampusphotos%2Fsiu%2Fcover.jpg%3Fsv%3D2018-03-28%26sr%3Db%26sig%3DBogXBqQb5%252BJr%252F7hpVjEChdOf6ywQv7Zcmr%252BL4ID4mE0%253D%26st%3D2022-10-20T15%253A43%253A03Z%26se%3D2022-10-20T15%253A58%253A03Z%26sp%3Dr&fb_obo=1&utld=windows.net&stp=c0.5000x0.5000f_dst-jpg_flffffff_p476x24