soon.\nWe can pick you up when you reach here (Amtrac station/nearby places) and drop to your apartment. Its a common practice here, yet we are thinking to make it sure that, everyone get a ride once they reach here.\n\nSo, you can share the projected date and time of your arrival.\n\nHopefully, we can make an arrangement for you😊😊.\nHave a safe trip🤘🏻", "Congratulations and Welcome to all upcoming Salukis!\nThis post is specially for you guys. Hopefully, many of you already got the visa (or yet to get) and planning to be here in C'dale soon.\nWe can pick you up when you reach here (Amtrac station/nearby places) and drop to your apartment. Its a common practice here, yet we are thinking to make it sure that, everyone get a ride once they reach here.\n\nSo, you can share the projected date and time of your arrival.\n\nHopefully, we can make an arrangement for you😊😊.\nHave a safe trip🤘🏻", '', None, datetime.datetime(2022, 7, 27, 15, 40, 50), 1658954450, None, 'https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An-SJYN61eefFdoaV8pa0G_5_APCa0prZaqkZGXpCFeUCLCg89UPOqSkSZxJkLy0hAKKpUIPEB91mo9yBBfcAqcwmpEu5jN_jmJufFtJoVJCUklu.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBqLFfpc9k8Z06mHav2CcJWt4GECcU-aJii20gzgqf9BA&oe=6576209F&_nc_sid=7da55a', [], [], ['https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An-SJYN61eefFdoaV8pa0G_5_APCa0prZaqkZGXpCFeUCLCg89UPOqSkSZxJkLy0hAKKpUIPEB91mo9yBBfcAqcwmpEu5jN_jmJufFtJoVJCUklu.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBqLFfpc9k8Z06mHav2CcJWt4GECcU-aJii20gzgqf9BA&oe=6576209F&_nc_sid=7da55a', 'https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An_UvxJXg9tdnLU3Y5qjPi0200MLilhzPXUgxzGjQzUMaNcmjdZA6anyrngvkdub33NZzZhd51fpCAEzNHFhko5aKRFP5fS1w_lKwYrzcNLupv27.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBaIyI1GghPTHlZudMsYtMW_pWuCi6_JPXo0hOvwZ0xIg&oe=65761BB9&_nc_sid=7da55a'], ['Love', 'Like'], None, None, None, None, None, None, None, None, None, 8, 2, 0, 'https://m.facebook.com/groups/1590338747870221/permalink/3235424773361602/', None, [{'link': 'https://m.facebook.com/groups/1590338747870221/permalink/3235424773361602/?m_ent