ll have cuisines as well. No need to worry about anything. However, because it is hot outside it is better to take sun glass, umbrella, blanket to sit on and enough liquid to keep us hydrated.\n\nWe are expecting to see you all tomorrow.\n\nThank You.\n\nSumaiya Binta Islam\nGraduate Assistant\nStudy Abroad Program\nCenter for International Education", "Hello All,\n\nHope you are doing well in this hot summer.\nThe International Student Council is organizing a Summer Picnic event on Saturday, June 25th from 11:00 - 2:00 pm at Bucky's Haven, SIU campus, Carbondale. All international students, faculty, staff, guests, and friends are welcome! The event is open and free to everyone and will host a variety of international cuisines, international music & dancing, games, etc.\n\nThere will be 5 games -\n\n1) connecting the world on chart\n2) musical paper\n3) passing ball\n4) couple dance\n5) tag of war\n\nWe will have cuisines as well. No need to worry about anything. However, because it is hot outside it is better to take sun glass, umbrella, blanket to sit on and enough liquid to keep us hydrated.\n\nWe are expecting to see you all tomorrow.\n\nThank You.\n\nSumaiya Binta Islam\nGraduate Assistant\nStudy Abroad Program\nCenter for International Education", '', None, datetime.datetime(2022, 6, 24, 11, 36, 22), 1656088582, 'https://scontent-ord5-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/290295917_3175656506024540_7075222635477301168_n.jpg?stp=cp0_dst-jpg_e15_fr_q65&_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=5f2048&efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&_nc_ohc=gYGYSSyZ1CwAX8q6SmD&tn=PKBvE-4fpoK4f5Ih&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-1.xx&oh=00_AfAtb2Jcimc6WIhG-1pNncR9zkDWvGKqQqpUXqTC6Dd6AA&oe=655335A9&manual_redirect=1', 'https://scontent-ord5-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/290295917_3175656506024540_7075222635477301168_n.jpg?stp=cp0_dst-jpg_e15_p320x320_q65&_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=5f2048&efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&_nc_ohc=gYGYSSyZ1CwAX8q6SmD&tn=PKBvE-4fpoK4f5Ih&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-1.xx&oh=00_AfDtdkUuk1l8r3qLNRZndwwzxa5dBbyNEBwIw2rMIgk0lQ&