/11/2022 from\n3 PM - 5 PM\nVenue : Student Center, CD activity Room, 3rd Floor.', 'Dear All,\nGreetings!\nHope the new semester is going well for everyone.\nWe are going to have a general MEETING this FRIDAY (02/11/2022) regarding our upcoming events and activities. This will be much like a casual get together where we can share our thoughts and suggestions. Also, we want to discuss about the International Talent Show and Food Competition.\nYour presence is highly appreciated.\nThank You.\n\nMeeting date and time: Friday, 02/11/2022 from\n3 PM - 5 PM\nVenue : Student Center, CD activity Room, 3rd Floor.', '', None, datetime.datetime(2022, 2, 9, 16, 1, 14), 1644444074, None, 'https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An_UvxJXg9tdnLU3Y5qjPi0200MLilhzPXUgxzGjQzUMaNcmjdZA6anyrngvkdub33NZzZhd51fpCAEzNHFhko5aKRFP5fS1w_lKwYrzcNLupv27.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBaIyI1GghPTHlZudMsYtMW_pWuCi6_JPXo0hOvwZ0xIg&oe=65761BB9&_nc_sid=7da55a', [], [], ['https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An_UvxJXg9tdnLU3Y5qjPi0200MLilhzPXUgxzGjQzUMaNcmjdZA6anyrngvkdub33NZzZhd51fpCAEzNHFhko5aKRFP5fS1w_lKwYrzcNLupv27.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBaIyI1GghPTHlZudMsYtMW_pWuCi6_JPXo0hOvwZ0xIg&oe=65761BB9&_nc_sid=7da55a'], ['Like'], None, None, None, None, None, None, None, None, None, 4, 2, 0, 'https://m.facebook.com/groups/1590338747870221/permalink/3111269445777136/', None, [{'link': 'https://m.facebook.com/groups/1590338747870221/permalink/3111269445777136/?m_entstream_source=group&refid=18&_ft_=encrypted_tracking_data.0AY_y6SvUFWR8n7Om6PldJEApLeWLdrOd0c7OH8puc-fLHFXjIpFsmabq8_EOdA68Ygzb8hMUDHGezFPNAf7Mwy4YL3HSYt2MA-QjPZqs3NR_K0pL2s46QsoOt-ujWzA7wmAA5S8Do96FTnlsUVPWOzrX4N9k1IMoPYB06kFFD-DftnhB0oi6nVzs_txKjejMNTlevQ0fdHyaRwdnor1vjgNhcEGWY91XOThPKfS0qgxTipdVyLaNgF-EGcJbVyIO03lzeakT_fYBIJyJ8FWw8Y-RkfOYqurA-r3A7OA0q8iJyC7-1Z4P6bbE2PwT7Jw3ZrZPgbP47nCJsk0j3lWEY46pzE06mgiCgPqmiSj7gzQT23bMZbjX77YvV2ZMLqlvigyePPBtpkrsxa9b3Qw5Q9WX7Tei8JMAYjqRF2xDGJnzZvrsKBBpG33R7uSpTV2GqhfIwC8YM4NTfjsJpTMp5A7vOUYq40qL0ceipCHgovq