: 'Sadia Afrin Joba', 'link': '/sadiaafrin.joba.9?eav=AfZKS3Vyqp2RhSBSNfpbAbozlhJjczdRl_fkpumrYMzhe81R886ABFI1mr6DkPbgQKM&fref=pb&paipv=0'}, {'name': 'Jahangir Alam', 'link': '/jahangir.alam.cse.buet?eav=AfYfTG_hOLi9jc1jUTsymf-o9wdS1TV2U5-ReiPjkLLiG7JZduJapcEJaN3p6abFM98&fref=pb&paipv=0'}, {'name': 'Md Ishtiak Hossain', 'link': '/amishtiak?eav=AfbjMNw62Xy1Dz4r5n0eENf1V-DEOa5EUtbEdd-RK-q1JCq9cqUhFrWACzpF5ns9iLQ&fref=pb&paipv=0'}], None, None, '10232168307456101', ['10232168307456101'], False, 'Asir Faisal is with Zarif Hossain and 3 others.'])dict_values(['3018196041751144', 'Dear all,\nHere is an announcement. We have decided to participate in Concession Stand at an upcoming football game on 16th October. By working a concession stand, BSA (RSO) will get the opportunity to make about 10% back from concession stand sales or around $300. It is an amazing chance to make funds for our association, as well as the enthusiasts will get to engage in a fun social event.\n\nThus, We need a list of 10 volunteers, among them 8 volunteers will work for about 6.5 hours on a particular day. Interested people can either put a comment here, or inbox me/ Shujon Mehedi Hasan for more details in this regard. In the comment section, I have attached the mandate file for better understanding the rules and regulations. Your participation is highly appreciated and acknowledged.\n\nTake care and Thank You.', 'Dear all,\nHere is an announcement. We have decided to participate in Concession Stand at an upcoming football game on 16th October. By working a concession stand, BSA (RSO) will get the opportunity to make about 10% back from concession stand sales or around $300. It is an amazing chance to make funds for our association, as well as the enthusiasts will get to engage in a fun social event.\n\nThus, We need a list of 10 volunteers, among them 8 volunteers will work for about 6.5 hours on a particular day. Interested people can either put a comment here, or inbox me/ Shujon Mehedi Hasan for more details in this regard. In the comment section, I have attached the mandate file for better understanding the rules and regulations. Your participation is highly appreciated and acknowledged.\n\nTake care and Thank You.', '', None, datetime.datetime(2021, 10, 6, 14, 12, 1), 1633547521, None, 'https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An_UvxJXg9tdnLU3Y5qjPi0200MLilhzPXUgxzGjQzUMaNcmjdZA6anyrngvkdub33NZzZhd51fpCAEzNHFhko5aKRFP5fS1w_lKwYrzcNLupv27.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBaIyI1GghPTHlZudMsYtMW_pWuCi6_JPXo0hOvwZ0xIg&oe=65761BB9&_nc_sid=7da55a', [], [], ['https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/m1/v/t6/An_UvxJXg9tdnLU3Y5qjPi0200MLilhzPXUgxzGjQzUMaNcmjdZA6anyrngvkdub33NZzZhd51fpCAEzNHFhko5aKRFP5fS1w_lKwYrzcNLupv27.png?ccb=10-5&oh=00_AfBaIyI1GghPTHlZudMsYtMW_pWuCi6_JPXo0hOvwZ0xIg&oe=65761BB9&_nc_sid=7da55a'], ['Like'], None, None, None, None, None, None, None, None, None, 2, 3, 0, 'https://m.facebook.com/groups/1590338747870221/permalink/3018196041751144/', None, [{'link': 'https://m.facebook.com/groups/1590338747870221/permalink/3018196041751144/?refid=18&paipv=0&eav=AfayrBZc9gyDk5-2sFNsyNefND2ckNHGBFy2bHx36k0foSB80Htydyp05iDiycUzHR4', 'text': 'More'}, {'link': '/shujon?groupid=1590338747870221&eav=AfYCEpCH-UwI3YmyIK99yDP2a9VnwkVMi_3Bx743-4YVehpaXriVshoEUbuu9gcFEcs&refid=18&_ft_=encrypted_tracking_data.0AY_WiokvHNmkGj0GLeWb-GAfO2ysl67u32oJqxR5Lw7zp4LD3GoNuVz5A3p-FQ7o5sRGDAbPTuDlR6nsEgxjKBNzWepOGrJZ_I8chdKM0b_f5c-HXFNV7H9OosXlSza0sFV9Fl-44LI0HxPPsNwpkvZZP1QlSNbWjr7EV8RYsw93okPDkUu5iLpjxDKyWshS_jr6dO_9aAoSTqOlIAkb3PcccW6K5zMceb78JoYvR7cdQuq-1EI__TYi4QBAfZr_5mZsc9Q-JqHRbLglDXTX4NGQwI4Lcagl153HFwjkoZGKuEKR9qly78h3X-76aL0O3UUtt6vEwD-8gzJAa43oj6S-HmQg8O3Zt1XTr13iGGQdMwcLXfZyNLoTHzB8MqdE0epKb_sJ_2-jUBSM1IFiAROa2D2xvaUIxxS2aXl6pzzyuz3TqK2ljXb-EanjFFpp9oAuXRpKJlPLAQMNxzxfGYJsVFTLAFus_DrZvcE9VTVpbEylSTG8XafrYKxoEOtNX4e_nnkO8gtosQBwq3R_nadqyaWiZjkxCd9tJQINR9L8ZqgMg4nFj-2mFjJT1SfONvRzy7XXG3915N4tMCOKNOZ4yzkGUFvejCQ57g7uJ6h-Cogf9LwZcM378RUIdt1xHCNlXd7zYAA4zqCnp-qOXqfgRdjRHt4y5zQ