 more information please contact global.salukis@siu.edu\n\n#ISC #SIU #SIUC #centerforinternationalstudentssiu #iscsiuc', 'Join us to celebrate the diversity, inclusiveness, and cultures represented at SIUC and in the region during the 2021 International Festival! 🌎\n\nHave an awesome talent you want to show off? The International Student Council (ISC) and the Center for International Education (CIE) at Southern Illinois University Carbondale are excited to announce the first-ever 2021 International Festival Virtual Talent Show on April 9th at 6:00pm! 🌎 All talents are welcome such as singing, dancing, etc, and feel free to perform with a group. If interested in submitting your video rather than performing live, fill out the form below. Please keep videos between 1-3 minutes long if possible.\n\n🏆 Prizes will be given to the top three winners of $50, $30, and $20 in the form of a Visa gift card. We cannot wait to see everyone’s talents! The DEADLINE to submit is: April 7, 2021.\n\n-Please register at Zoom for the live event: Talent Show 2021 - April 9th, 6pm https://zoom.us/meeting/register/tJUvfu2orjIvGdbN4OB6RFazxS0dh8RIZTxN\n-Please sign up here to participate and submit your video: Talent Show Form https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf2HLMmQkmHEqgjORtbbVxdDYcgbRT3VbrkD0YhdJb_cV25tg/viewform\n\nFor more information please contact global.salukis@siu.edu\n\n#ISC #SIU #SIUC #centerforinternationalstudentssiu #iscsiuc', '', None, datetime.datetime(2021, 3, 30, 19, 41, 25), 1617151285, None, 'https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/166362065_10160714350503362_671521180322651229_n.png?stp=dst-png_p320x320&_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=7afa59&efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&_nc_ohc=KEBPwW2Nhl0AX_tY4NM&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-2.xx&oh=00_AfBPvtsvgzH9xqZd96rhPn53xZFRfvcMK1hMsV1qSqklgA&oe=65762A70', [], [], ['https://scontent-ord5-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/166362065_10160714350503362_671521180322651229_n.png?stp=dst-png_p320x320&_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=7afa59&efg=eyJpIjoidCJ